snippet.title: A Visual Novel - 40 Days and 40 Nights of Rain
snippet.description:
As I upload this it is 11:53 PM, Christmas day. Though I probably won't make it to my deadline, I'm still happy I got this video done. I can't believe it's been so long, and I wish I could've done more. But that's just me rambling on. I'm sad this probably won't make Christmas, but who cares, what's done is done.

Thank you for watching!
